This is a movie directed at guys, kind of. . . .  We haven't got a clue when it comes to relationships.  Even when we do manage to get something right, we don't know when to quit!  I showed this nine minute movie as a prelude to my Defensive Driver Training Course for the county.  I got everyone's attention!  My best class ever.  Whether training or leisure, this film is sure to leave a lasting impression.
